@baseUrl = http://localhost:80
@topK = 5

### RAG-000 Rebuild embeddings before a full regression run
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/knowledge/embeddings/rebuild

### RAG-001 3栋本周六会停水吗？
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/community/customer-service/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "communityId": 1,
  "question": "3栋本周六会停水吗？",
  "topK": {{topK}}
}

